A vintage 1950s-style illustration of a grand Art Deco skyscraper shown in cross-section, revealing multiple floors with increasingly simpler interiors as you descend from top to bottom. The penthouse level features elaborate futuristic technology with glowing screens and sleek furnishings, while middle floors show progressively more modest equipment, and the ground floor displays basic functional furniture and simple mechanical devices. The building stands against a warm sepia-toned sky with dramatic sunbeams. The architectural style combines retro-futurism with classic poster art aesthetics, using muted oranges, teals, and cream colors with bold linework and subtle halftone textures characteristic of mid-century commercial illustration.
